item.title: Starlite Pop Orchestra - White Christmas, song (from 'Holiday Inn') (Vocal Version)
item.description:
Ukulele play along of White Christmas
A nice easy version as it is a slow tempo, ideal for beginners.
Using the chords: G Am D C G7 Cm Em
Strum Pattern: D DU D DU
This video is meant for educational purposes.
No copyright infringement intended
